overview: Set in the closed and poisonous world of an isolated privileged private school for boys, Dartworth takes us deep into the power structures in the school, where the boys operate a counter world, entirely of their own, making and within the Prefects control. When their prank goes horribly wrong, the battle between the Prefects and Mitchell becomes a race to survive as the police begin to uncover the surprising truth.
title: Dartworth
